[I] A free and open source molecular editor and visualization tool

[T] A free and open source molecular editor and visualization tool. Designed
[T] for students and advanced researchers alike. Used in computational
[T] chemistry, molecular modeling, chemistry education, bioinformatics,
[T] materials science, and more.

[U] https://two.avogadro.cc/

[A] Avogadro
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 2.0.0

[SRC] .
[D] 392d9cecd40b61f3a161652e776a98c3ee5378be93e0a6b6e6198d8a avogadrolibs-2.0.0.tar.gz https://github.com/OpenChemistry/avogadrolibs/archive/2.0.0/
[D] b08f6fcc30033e1ff8e4fa3758e996c12fd624e0a261f8892ff6e6d6 avogadroapp-2.0.0.tar.gz https://github.com/OpenChemistry/avogadroapp/archive/2.0.0/

rungpepinstall=0 runpysetup=0
pkginstalled qt5base && var_append cmakeopt ' ' -DQT_VERSION=5
pkginstalled qt6base && var_append cmakeopt ' ' -DQT_VERSION=6

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' "-I$root`pkgprefix includedir glu`"
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' "-L$root`pkgprefix libdir glu`"
